\qj \hyphpar0 \cbpat0 {\sa60\sb60\li720\ri0\fi-360\sl288\slmult1 \f10 \fs20 \cf1 \b0 \i0 \strike0 \ul0 (a) the "contractor" and "proprietor" of the site within the meaning of F&IUO and the F&IUR;\par}
}

{\pard \fi-360 \li720 \ls5 
